.TH LOA-UNDO 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
undo \- Revert the latest change
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> undo
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Reverts the most recent mutating action in the current app session.
.TP
Undo history depth is limited (default 100 changes).
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> undo
